Go bindings for GLUT: https://github.com/rhencke/glut

If you are using Linux, please ensure you have installed GLUT or freeglut.

To install:
    go get -u github.com/difarem/glut

To run the examples:
    go get github.com/difarem/glut/examples/asteroids
    asteroids
    go get github.com/difarem/glut/examples/fontdemo
    fontdemo
    go get github.com/difarem/glut/examples/simple
    simple
